Distribution. Western Atlantic—USA (Florida), Antilles, Colombia , Venezuela , and Brazil (Pará, Pernambuco , Alagoas , Bahia , Espírito Santo , Rio de Janeiro , São Paulo , Santa Catarina) ( Melo 1996 , 1998;
Mantelatto et al. 2004b
;
Almeida et al. 2007a
;
Coelho et al . 2008
).

Remarks. Previous records on the coast of São Paulo include Ubatuba (
Mantelatto et al. 2004b
;
Alves et al. 2012b
), Ilha das Couves (
Assugeni et al. 2017
), Ilha das Palmas (
Magalhães et al . 2017
), and Ilha Vitória (
Alves et al. 2012a
). This species was included in the genus
Damithrax ( Windsor & Felder 2014 )
that was posteriorly invalidated and
M. tortugae
was back assigned to
Mithrax ( Windsor & Felder 2017 )
. Sequences accession number (GenBank): CCDB 5024—16S ( MF490177 ), CCDB 4130—COI ( MF490081 ) (
Mantelatto et al. 2018a
).
